Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.43,0:22:40.33,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever Wherever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.48,0:22:49.67,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新たな旅立ち 迎えよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.70,0:22:59.71,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失いかけていた　Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.71,0:23:04.69,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼び覚ましたconfined　in you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.84,0:23:14.38,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共にした日々を強く握り緊め
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:19.55,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever Wherever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.76,0:23:23.74,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互いに寄り添い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.98,0:23:28.65,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れる事などない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.89,0:23:34.07,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇が二人分かつとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.24,0:23:39.35,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確かな鼓動が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.53,0:23:43.40,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう告げているから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.58,0:23:48.18,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再び出会えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.68,0:24:00.55,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想いよ　どうか君と共に

Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.43,0:22:40.33,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever Wherever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.48,0:22:49.67,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎接新的启程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.70,0:22:59.71,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追逐着失落之物　Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.71,0:23:04.69,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唤醒被囚禁中的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.84,0:23:14.38,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力握紧朝夕共处的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:19.55,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever Wherever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.76,0:23:23.74,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要互相靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.98,0:23:28.65,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无害怕之事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.89,0:23:34.07,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使黑暗终将分开你我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.24,0:23:39.35,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明确的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.53,0:23:43.40,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣告了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.58,0:23:48.18,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到与你再次相遇那天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.68,0:24:00.55,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望这份思念能伴你左右
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.55,0:24:12.55,op_chi,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.02,0:00:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.21,0:00:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我来到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…Phantom吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏菲小姐 已经在里面了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个箱子突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛西尔老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这是怎么了 为什么会在箱子里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为一名教师不能对学生的危机置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我拼上性命进行的潜入调查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请冷静一下 你说的学生是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说 维多利加同学有麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加同学又被父亲传唤去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就待在这 赛西尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再继续涉入了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉似乎和往常不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过因为是在箱子里 所以不太明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城君？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:47.68,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(658,546)}受Phantom的幽灵指引
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你身在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管将要到来的暴风雨有多么猛烈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 你为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…你真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会找到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…维多利加 慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.14,0:05:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去父亲 亚伯特·德·布洛瓦侯爵那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得好 我的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是让你的力量为我等所用之时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我思考过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么灵异部会在那么多年后还想揭发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可·萝丝事件的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你们已经有所头绪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没有确定性的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想找到证据 并以此抓住犯人的把柄对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后 得到更高的地位以及权力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个国家拥有此等影响力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正是这起事件的真正犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才不愧是我亲爱的灰色之狼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可·萝丝事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前一次大战之前不久 1914春
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从法国来了一名使者想面见可可王妃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王陛下将身在乡间别墅的王妃接进了王宫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.69,0:07:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在房间被人发现时 王妃已经是一具无头尸体了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人在之前进过王妃的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了国王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是当然 他没有持有任何可疑的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:08:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在几乎同一时刻 在王妃的乡间别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说在目击者中也有科学院的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后事件就陷入了僵局
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要维多利加来解决这个事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不解决这件事的话 她就无法回学园去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是父亲大人的决定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不觉得她会有无法解决的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用如此担心啊 小男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎片…混沌的碎片聚齐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报纸上的报道 当时的调查报告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料都应该收集齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这种程度的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加早就已经知道真相了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去收集起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的话就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是不将碎片带来 维多利加就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要和维多利加一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等着我 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道柯蒂丽亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂丽亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 柯蒂丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这个人果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加的…母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:10:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是16年前的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不错的舞女啊 突然就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.03,0:10:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…她母亲待过的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这地方 维多利加她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 刚刚有个女孩子也看着这张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长的非常像 一瞬间还以为是本人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王妃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么王妃的照片会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女孩是尼可蕾·露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和可可王妃长的很像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人叫做「平民区的蓝蔷薇」 是个非常有人气的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平民区的…蓝蔷薇…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个很开朗的好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个孩子也无缘无故不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在这行里也是常有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快将谜解开吧 灰色之狼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的 混沌的碎片还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料已经全部集齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上根本没有灰色之狼不知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也要集齐了碎片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这些的话就算想再构成也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招秘书？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 1900年的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多24年前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个吗 我记得很清楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像条件是金发蓝瞳的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连脚的尺寸也指定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面试结束后 房间就处理掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是群奇怪的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫尼可蕾·露露的女演员…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去应征了刚刚那个秘书的募集后 就这样失踪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 果然很可疑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微调查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 这也是为了维多利加呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…「平民区的蓝蔷薇」?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的和事件有关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一种有关系的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是什么时候 我看见她坐上了一辆豪华的马车哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼可蕾不再上台表演 也已经有10年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是成了不知道是什么地方的贵族还是有钱人的情妇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来我也听说了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来尼可蕾不见 也已经有10年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去应征秘书 贵族的情妇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同学 让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很难得啊 也要买点特产回去给苏菲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给苏菲小姐的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们经常一起来购物 要是知道我一个人来了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会生气的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏菲小姐的话 现在就在苏瓦伦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 她来看可可·萝丝的那个戏剧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是坐她的摩托车来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不约我一起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将相处10年的老友扔在一边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么和久城同学一起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相处10年的老友？你们是在哪里认识的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌久城同学 所以不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 那个…老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏菲就更讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是得感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 什么时候会出场呢 可可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼可蕾·露露？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说您是她的超级fan
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 所以真是个大打击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说她死了的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么你们不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼可蕾她已经死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 上面写着 1900年亡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…尼克蕾小姐失踪那年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是秘书募集那年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在那10年后被人目击到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请现在马上住手 就算做这种事也是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也好好看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:16:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女儿 你的妹妹身上所寄宿的真正力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人 父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用药草使感觉变得敏锐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而单调的回音和蜡烛的摇晃不过是为了增强效果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么灵异啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不完全是科学嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们既没票 剧场旁边还有守卫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊 久城君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官应该会来才对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开谜团吧 灰色之狼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在仪式结束前 不许离开这房间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你就待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了 久城君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰色之狼 解开谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答 犯人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人手法呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对抗我时的那份气势去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:17:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 住…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开灯 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼狼在里面这扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:19:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 太好了 太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 这个事件…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不牵连我 你…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想牵扯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不也挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个渐渐卷入你所有一切的 麻烦的…朋友存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神圣的仪式被玷污了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那个人赶出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:21:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 就算现在于此挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无法从父亲的束缚中挣脱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了生存下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而展现力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会解开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我来解开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会解开可可·萝丝事件的谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给美丽的狼之母 送上祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.69,0:21:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会想要调查尼可蕾·露露？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:22:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我觉得这事应该能让你开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为无聊秀才的你来说算是做得不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.31,0:22:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就表扬你一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人的许可下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 你想去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.31,0:22:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去墓地 挖出尼可蕾·露露的棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.93,0:24:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可·萝丝的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的帷幕终于要拉开了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.79,0:24:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可 就让我在你的人生里装饰上花朵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.14,0:24:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在混沌中盛开的 名叫真实谎言的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.27,0:24:20.07,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(625,559)}圣夜的钟声追赶时刻
